`del_all_files(main_dir, confirmation=True)` <div style="float: right; font-size: 15px;">[source](https://github.com/Mr-TalhaIlyas/FMUtils/blob/722bf3f7312eb076b1be5108601ba32a8d2339dc/scripts/fmutils.py#L137)</div>
